snippet.title: Valkyria Chronicles 4 - New Features Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: War, while destructive, breeds innovation. Valkyria Chronicles 4 introduces new units, battlefield-defining command orders, and much more. Get a quick look at a few of these features in this trailer!
